Class ExceptionlessVariableVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.ExceptionlessVariableVisitor

    InputParserVisitor

    public abstract class ExceptionlessVariableVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements VariableVisitor

    Base class for a VariableVisitor that doesn't throw any exceptions.

    Exists mainly for the convenient visit(Variable).
